Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:33.03,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}a boy runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:36.87,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}When he lets go,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:47.76,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}it disappears into the sound of the wind in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:55.85,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}The kindness that he once saw is now gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:06.78,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,0)}He steps forward alone, looking only at his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:22.17,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,0)\3c&HCB6D14&\bord2\blur2}He always listened to the song that disappeared by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:37.43,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(0,500)}He chased forever those footprints we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I feel that everything that has happened so far was a trial for me to become your real mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.77,Note,,0,0,0,,[Sign: Misuzu-chin is resting]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feet not moving and you losing your memory were all trials for us to redo everything from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll massage it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! It hurts, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My wings... hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, Misuzu will begin to forget about me and about you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, after seeing her final dream, she'll probably die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If she falls asleep, if she dreams, she'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:00:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll go to the summer festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see the summer festival with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a dinosaur's baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about chicks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's probably a stall selling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I buy... a dinosaur?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's eat something delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make tomorrow a really fun day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So get better, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the day of the summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, God,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way they'd hold the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that a god can exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What did this girl do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't she wait like a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she looking forward to the summer festival a lot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't she rewarded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I'm never able to give you anything, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the dinosaur's baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were watching all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the dinosaur, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go get it together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a happy memory for the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's treasure it and raise it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend is here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We can reach our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my birthday present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't give it to you all this time we've been together, but will you accept it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes "Gao!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't slept for a long time, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asleep just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to sleep with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you sleep and dream, your pain will worsen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't hurt for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It really doesn't hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sleep and recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it good, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you did your best,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you were rewarded, right, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a cracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for lying to you, Mummy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but you wouldn't rest unless I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write in my diary.
