Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your body hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That means it'll be a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy, I had a dream last night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You start hurting whenever you have dreams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hurt anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, my dreams will end today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's really nothing wrong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't hurt anywhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The freeloader said something about you having your last dream, but that was a mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was apprehensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Those days were like nightmares to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's finally over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you to stop crying anymore; I'm a crybaby too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:37.70,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Said in kansai-ben; Misuzu is imitating her mother]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't cry when there's nothing to be sad about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream last night was about a dinosaur with wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was flying, looking like it felt good, and saying "Gao."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was flying even higher than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked behind my shoulder;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I had wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They were pure white wings, and I was flying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was a sad dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the saddest dream in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the end of my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I'm going to be by your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,always and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, isn't it a really nice day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.38,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Again, Misuzu says "really" in kansai-ben]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it feels really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells like summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of smell does it have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's also true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy's smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I don't want it to reek with my smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells a lot like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this summer smelled a lot like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of my precious mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If it reeked of that, it would suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That would suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a good smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's hot all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Misuzu, do you want me to guess what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to drink juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone would have been able to guess that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like this one, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I recommend the Gel-lun juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gooey?! It's hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I want juice like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You drink this by squeezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it isn't bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a summer vacation with just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right; we'll play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to go on ahead by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Sora with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this far enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy, keep standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, don't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to walk over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Mummy, you're my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you and Sora are the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait as long as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, slow and steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep working hard like that, you'll definitely recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I did my best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go to my goal now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, after you reach me, we'll go home and play cards or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,my goal, the goal I've been aiming at for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I... did my best, so it's enough now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can rest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been hurting all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to start recovering, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The bad dreams were supposed to have ended, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was able to finish everything, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll go to my goal, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we start our lives anew yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take it back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the happy life that should have started ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take it back, starting now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our happiness has just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we did everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A lifetime's worth of happiness was crammed into this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of things I still want to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,lots of things I want to do with my beloved Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All of that starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time... the summer vacation when I thought I'd do my best,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the summer vacation that started on the day I met Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though lots happened, even though it hurt sometimes or was painful sometimes, I'm glad I tried my hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my goal was to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I wasn't all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to my goal now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying it all starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally reached it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The place I've always looked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The place of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The place of... eternal happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How to escape from living alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need friends, new clothes, luxuries, or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being with you is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.60,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an9}[Kamio Haruko, Class 1-4]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's live together happily at the Kamio house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent the days since then crying and crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've run out of tears to shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't families great?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The happiest and the most painful,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's precisely what it means for people to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived together with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We were brash, ragged, strong, and weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to make no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so much that it almost hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You would understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I might not be great, I'm her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to quit my current job and work at the neighbourhood daycare centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to live surrounded by many families from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll visit occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My vacation is ending too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.83,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\an1\fs35\frz23.877\fnSegoe Print\c&H4E4E4E&\move(193,472,130,554,0,2364)\t(\fscx115\fscy115)}This summer vacation, \Nmany fun things happened. \NI had Mummy buy me \Na dinosaur baby. \NI'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten quite big.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you a different crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're Sora, I'll have to scold you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, "You're still here? She's not here anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,since you have wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky is a forever unreachable place for us humans, as we have no wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you must fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For us, since we have no wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,People's dreams and wishes, return them all to this sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, we'll be able to live peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be nice if we can see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, best of luck to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I was looking at the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which had always been filled with a sad colour,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that endless blue that continues forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the girl who returned to that infinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the girl who is still all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will go on a voyage to continue searching for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And someday, I will bring her back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...to welcome a new beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My child, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The story that I'm about to tell you is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a long, long story of a journey that will be passed down from parent to child endlessly, starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We continue to inherit the memories of the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We see and hear every event that takes place on this planet and then pass it down, from mother to child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The memories of the stars must be eternally happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When the sky is covered by hatred and war,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this planet will wail and grieve, and everything will return to the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually reaching Apocalypse...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...is a fate that cannot be avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, please give happy memories to the last child who bears the stars' memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun will set soon, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Before it does, let's go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Check what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What you wanted to check for a long time:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what is beyond this shoreline.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not have said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I had a feeling you were thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, I want to go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do it now, we can find out what lies beyond there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To them, cruel days,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and to us, a beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:09.84,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\b1\pos(640,600)\blur0.5}The End
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Intruding while your master is changing is the epitome of disloyalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"You are forbidden to commit murder," was it?
